name: Bond-it
description: The quiz is about how well do you know a person?! This would be a very interactive and challenging game between the user and the person with whom he would like to play.

questions.question: Which chocolate do I love most ?
Where would I like to go with my life partner?
How would I like to call my partner?
What would make me most happy?
Where would I like to go in my vacation?
Which member of your friend group are you?
What would I do with an unexpected income of $1000?
What do I do to relax?

name: Flag up
description: FlagUp is a fun general knowledge game that tests your knowledge of flags around the world. This is the game in which you can test your flag knowledge. The quiz game, for example, provides you the images of flags in which you have to tell what is the country name

name: Iconic
description: Iconic is a fun game that test your knowledge about the icon that you see in this digital world

name: Colorista
description: Love playing with colors? Then we have something in store for you.Lets see how far your brain can handle this. Hit the play button and lets roll!
rules: Be quick to race to the top of the leaderboard! Time matters!
